        #top_car.topCar
          #car_itm_0
            p I have this nagging perception that the web is becoming more commoditized  every day.
          #car_itm_1
            p I believe in the open source hardware movement, and wan't to get involved.
          #car_itm_2
            p I go to a job interview at Makerbot.
          #car_itm_3
            p I blow the tech screen
          #car_itm_4
            p I can&apos;t explain closures, build custom events on the fly,
          #car_itm_5
            p without checking the internet, I can&apos;t tell how many subway stations there are in Manhattan
          #car_itm_6
            p I look to focus this disappointment into something positive.
          #car_itm_7
            p I know the web stack, I know how to build stuff.
          #car_itm_8
            p I learn all I can about Arduino, I get better at Javascript.
          #car_itm_9
            p I buy a bunch of electronic goodies from makershed.com.
          #car_itm_10
            p I build a toy robot for my son for his 4th birthday.
